    ('90000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000058', '88888888-8888-8888-8888-888888888881', N'Hong Kong Victoria Peak Tram View', N'Hong Kong Victoria Peak Tram View is a harbor skyline anchor for tram ride, harbor views, night photos, and compact landmark routing. Visitor mix: first-time visitors, families, skyline photographers, and evening-date crowds. Best fit: clear evenings, weekdays reduce queues; crowd level busy at sunset; budget mid; pace structured evening; group fit couples, families, solo photographers. It adds a globally legible skyline viewpoint with useful planning notes.', 22.2759, 114.1455, N'Peak Tram Lower Terminus', N'Hong Kong', N'HK', N'scenic', N'harbor skyline', N'["photo-worthy","date-night","worth-the-drive"]', 4.8, 59, 58, N'showcase:demo-spot-58', N'Hong Kong Victoria Peak Tram View', N'Peak Tram Lower Terminus, Hong Kong, Hong Kong Island, HK'),
    ('90000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000059', 'bbbbbbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbbbbbbbbb1', N'Porto Ribeira Tile-and-River Walk', N'Porto Ribeira Tile-and-River Walk is a river tiles anchor for riverside walk, tile facades, bridge views, and dinner routing. Visitor mix: city-break travelers, locals near the river, wine tourists, and couples. Best fit: spring/fall evenings are strongest; crowd level busy sunset and weekends; budget mid; pace slow evening; group fit couples, friends, solo photographers. It adds Porto as a high-demand but compact European route.', 41.1406, -8.611, N'Cais da Ribeira', N'Porto', N'PT', N'scenic', N'river tiles', N'["photo-worthy","date-night","lively"]', 4.8, 60, 59, N'showcase:demo-spot-59', N'Porto Ribeira Tile-and-River Walk', N'Cais da Ribeira, Porto, Norte, PT'),
    ('90000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000060', '88888888-8888-8888-8888-888888888881', N'Miyajima Floating Gate Ferry Day', N'Miyajima Floating Gate Ferry Day is a island shrine anchor for ferry day trip, shrine timing, tide-aware photos, and gentle island walking. Visitor mix: Japan rail travelers, families, shrine visitors, and photographers. Best fit: spring/fall and tide-aware windows are strongest; crowd level busy during holidays; budget mid; pace slow day trip; group fit families, couples, solo travelers. It adds Hiroshima/Miyajima with planning texture beyond Tokyo/Kyoto.', 34.2959, 132.3199, N'Miyajimacho', N'Hatsukaichi', N'JP', N'culture', N'island shrine', N'["photo-worthy","worth-the-drive","family-friendly"]', 4.9, 61, 60, N'showcase:demo-spot-60', N'Miyajima Floating Gate Ferry Day', N'Miyajimacho, Hatsukaichi, Hiroshima, JP'),
    ('90000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000061', '99999999-9999-9999-9999-999999999991', N'Amsterdam Canal Ring Golden Hour', N'Amsterdam Canal Ring Golden Hour is a canal evening anchor for canal photos, bridge walks, cafe timing, and low-stress orientation. Visitor mix: city-break visitors, locals biking home, couples, and museum travelers. Best fit: golden hour, spring/fall shoulder seasons; crowd level moderate, busy in peak summer; budget low-mid; pace slow evening; group fit couples, solo walkers, small groups. It gives Amsterdam a routeable scenic core that is not only nightlife.', 52.3676, 4.8841, N'Prinsengracht', N'Amsterdam', N'NL', N'scenic', N'canal evening', N'["photo-worthy","date-night","calm"]', 4.8, 62, 61, N'showcase:demo-spot-61', N'Amsterdam Canal Ring Golden Hour', N'Prinsengracht, Amsterdam, North Holland, NL'),
    ('90000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000062', 'dddddddd-dddd-dddd-dddd-ddddddddddd1', N'Istanbul Galata to Bosphorus Descent', N'Istanbul Galata to Bosphorus Descent is a hillside harbor anchor for tower views, steep streets, ferry links, and layered neighborhood browsing. Visitor mix: locals, international visitors, food walkers, and photographers. Best fit: spring/fall afternoons are strongest; crowd level busy midday and sunset; budget low-mid; pace active afternoon; group fit couples, friends, solo walkers comfortable with hills. It adds Istanbul with meaningful slope, ferry, and crowd context.', 41.0256, 28.9744, N'Galata Kulesi Sokak', N'Istanbul', N'TR', N'culture', N'hillside harbor', N'["photo-worthy","lively","worth-the-drive"]', 4.8, 63, 62, N'showcase:demo-spot-62', N'Istanbul Galata to Bosphorus Descent', N'Galata Kulesi Sokak, Istanbul, Istanbul, TR'),
    ('90000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000063', 'bbbbbbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbbbbbbbbb1', N'Dubai Creek Al Seef Night Walk', N'Dubai Creek Al Seef Night Walk is a creek lights anchor for creekside walking, dinner, heritage-style streets, and night photos. Visitor mix: families, stopover travelers, residents, and first-time visitors balancing old/new Dubai. Best fit: best at night, October through April; crowd level moderate-busy in cool months; budget mid; pace slow evening; group fit families, couples, groups. It makes Dubai more specific than malls and towers by using a creekside route.', 25.2633, 55.301, N'Al Seef St', N'Dubai', N'AE', N'scenic', N'creek lights', N'["family-friendly","date-night","photo-worthy"]', 4.7, 64, 63, N'showcase:demo-spot-63', N'Dubai Creek Al Seef Night Walk', N'Al Seef St, Dubai, Dubai, AE'),
    ('90000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000064', '88888888-8888-8888-8888-888888888881', N'Seoul Bukchon Hanok Ridge', N'Seoul Bukchon Hanok Ridge is a hanok lanes anchor for traditional lanes, viewpoint walking, cafe pairing, and respectful quiet routing. Visitor mix: culture travelers, photographers, locals passing through, and first-time Seoul visitors. Best fit: morning or weekday shoulder times are best; crowd level busy midday, residential quiet needed; budget low; pace slow morning; group fit solo travelers, couples, small respectful groups. It adds Seoul with clear local-respect and crowd guidance.', 37.5826, 126.983, N'Bukchon-ro 11-gil', N'Seoul', N'KR', N'culture', N'hanok lanes', N'["photo-worthy","calm","quick-stop"]', 4.7, 65, 64, N'showcase:demo-spot-64', N'Seoul Bukchon Hanok Ridge', N'Bukchon-ro 11-gil, Seoul, Seoul, KR'),
    ('90000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000065', '88888888-8888-8888-8888-888888888881', N'Kyoto Fushimi Inari Lower Gates', N'Kyoto Fushimi Inari Lower Gates is a torii trail anchor for shrine walk, torii photos, early timing, and optional hike extension. Visitor mix: Japan travelers, shrine visitors, hikers, photographers, and families. Best fit: dawn or early morning year-round; crowd level very busy after breakfast; budget low; pace active morning; group fit solo travelers, couples, families ready for stairs. It adds Kyoto with a classic place plus realistic timing advice.', 34.9671, 135.7727, N'68 Fukakusa Yabunouchicho', N'Kyoto', N'JP', N'culture', N'torii trail', N'["photo-worthy","worth-the-drive","solo-friendly"]', 4.9, 66, 65, N'showcase:demo-spot-65', N'Kyoto Fushimi Inari Lower Gates', N'68 Fukakusa Yabunouchicho, Kyoto, Kyoto, JP'),
    ('90000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000066', 'dddddddd-dddd-dddd-dddd-ddddddddddd1', N'Buenos Aires San Telmo Market Sunday', N'Buenos Aires San Telmo Market Sunday is a market tango anchor for market food, street music, antiques, and neighborhood walking. Visitor mix: locals, antiques browsers, food travelers, tango-curious visitors, and weekend groups. Best fit: Sunday late morning into afternoon; crowd level busy Sundays; budget low-mid; pace active Sunday; group fit friends, solo food travelers, couples. It adds Buenos Aires with a real market rhythm and social energy.', -34.621, -58.3731, N'Defensa 963', N'Buenos Aires', N'AR', N'food', N'market tango', N'["lively","budget-friendly","photo-worthy"]', 4.7, 67, 66, N'showcase:demo-spot-66', N'Buenos Aires San Telmo Market Sunday', N'Defensa 963, Buenos Aires, Buenos Aires, AR'),
    ('90000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000067', 'dddddddd-dddd-dddd-dddd-ddddddddddd1', N'Rio Sugarloaf Cable Car View', N'Rio Sugarloaf Cable Car View is a bay cable car anchor for cable car ride, bay views, sunset photos, and skyline orientation. Visitor mix: first-time Rio visitors, families, photographers, and sunset planners. Best fit: clear mornings or sunset, weather visibility matters; crowd level busy at sunset; budget mid-high; pace structured half-day; group fit families, couples, solo photographers. It adds a globally iconic viewpoint with weather-sensitive planning.', -22.9486, -43.1566, N'Av. Pasteur, 520', N'Rio de Janeiro', N'BR', N'scenic', N'bay cable car', N'["photo-worthy","worth-the-drive","date-night"]', 4.9, 68, 67, N'showcase:demo-spot-67', N'Rio Sugarloaf Cable Car View', N'Av. Pasteur, 520, Rio de Janeiro, Rio de Janeiro, BR'),
    ('90000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000068', 'bbbbbbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbbbbbbbbb1', N'Marrakech Jemaa el-Fnaa Food Edge', N'Marrakech Jemaa el-Fnaa Food Edge is a night market anchor for night-market energy, food stalls, orientation, and cautious group wandering. Visitor mix: international tourists, local vendors, families, and guided food walkers. Best fit: evening outside peak summer heat; crowd level very busy at night; budget low-mid; pace fast evening; group fit groups, couples comfortable with crowds, guided solo travelers. It adds Marrakech with practical crowd and pacing context.', 31.6258, -7.9892, N'Jemaa el-Fnaa', N'Marrakech', N'MA', N'food', N'night market', N'["lively","photo-worthy","group-friendly"]', 4.6, 69, 68, N'showcase:demo-spot-68', N'Marrakech Jemaa el-Fnaa Food Edge', N'Jemaa el-Fnaa, Marrakech, Marrakech-Safi, MA'),
    ('90000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000069', 'cccccccc-cccc-cccc-cccc-ccccccccccc1', N'Cairo Giza Plateau First Light', N'Cairo Giza Plateau First Light is a desert monuments anchor for monument visit, early photos, heat management, and guided routing. Visitor mix: international tourists, history travelers, families, guides, and photographers. Best fit: first light or early morning, cooler months easiest; crowd level busy and hot midday; budget mid; pace structured morning; group fit families, groups, solo history travelers with guides. It adds Cairo/Giza with high-recognition and real timing constraints.', 29.9792, 31.1342, N'Al Haram', N'Giza', N'EG', N'culture', N'desert monuments', N'["photo-worthy","worth-the-drive","family-friendly"]', 4.9, 70, 69, N'showcase:demo-spot-69', N'Cairo Giza Plateau First Light', N'Al Haram, Giza, Giza, EG'),
    ('90000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000070', '88888888-8888-8888-8888-888888888881', N'Kuala Lumpur Petronas Park Frame', N'Kuala Lumpur Petronas Park Frame is a tower park anchor for tower photos, park break, mall/dinner pairing, and easy transit access. Visitor mix: families, business travelers, stopover visitors, and evening walkers. Best fit: evening fountain windows and clear nights; crowd level busy at night; budget low-mid; pace short evening; group fit families, couples, solo stopover travelers. It adds a Southeast Asia stopover city with easy planner utility.', 3.1579, 101.7116, N'KLCC Park', N'Kuala Lumpur', N'MY', N'scenic', N'tower park', N'["photo-worthy","family-friendly","quick-stop"]', 4.8, 71, 70, N'showcase:demo-spot-70', N'Kuala Lumpur Petronas Park Frame', N'KLCC Park, Kuala Lumpur, Kuala Lumpur, MY'),
    ('90000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000071', '88888888-8888-8888-8888-888888888881', N'Macau Senado Square Heritage Walk', N'Macau Senado Square Heritage Walk is a heritage square anchor for Portuguese-style streets, snacks, photos, and compact day-trip routing. Visitor mix: day trippers, families, heritage walkers, and food snackers. Best fit: weekday mornings or late afternoon are easiest; crowd level busy midday; budget low-mid; pace balanced afternoon; group fit families, couples, small groups. It adds Macau as a compact cross-border heritage stop.', 22.1935, 113.5398, N'Largo do Senado', N'Macau', N'MO', N'culture', N'heritage square', N'["photo-worthy","quick-stop","family-friendly"]', 4.6, 72, 71, N'showcase:demo-spot-71', N'Macau Senado Square Heritage Walk', N'Largo do Senado, Macau, Macau Peninsula, MO'),
    ('90000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000072', 'bcbcbcbc-bcbc-bcbc-bcbc-bcbcbcbcbc01', N'Ubud Campuhan Ridge Dawn Walk', N'Ubud Campuhan Ridge Dawn Walk is a ricefield ridge anchor for dawn walk, greenery, cafe finish, and low-cost outdoor reset. Visitor mix: wellness travelers, local walkers, photographers, and slow-travel visitors. Best fit: dawn, dry-season mornings are easiest; crowd level moderate after sunrise; budget low; pace slow morning; group fit solo travelers, couples, small groups. It adds Bali with a quiet nature-first alternative to beach-only planning.', -8.504, 115.2524, N'Jalan Bangkiang Sidem', N'Ubud', N'ID', N'nature', N'ricefield ridge', N'["calm","photo-worthy","solo-friendly"]', 4.8, 73, 72, N'showcase:demo-spot-72', N'Ubud Campuhan Ridge Dawn Walk', N'Jalan Bangkiang Sidem, Ubud, Bali, ID');
